data.description: Welcome home to this stunning 3-beds /2-baths property! Step into the beautiful, tiled eat-in kitchen with a bay window. Enjoy the granite countertops, backsplash & extra cabinets. Water-resistant vinyl flooring throughout. The master bedroom/bath includes his/her closets and updated vanities. This home is equipped with accordion hurricane shutters, a newer roof (only 5 years old), AC & water heater (4 years old), and an updated auto sprinkler system (2023). Relax on the tastefully tiled, covered/screened patio-the perfect spot to unwind and enjoy the breeze. Outside, explore banana, coconut, mango & lemon trees in a fully fenced backyard on a quiet cul-de-sac in Saratoga Lakes. The community offers a pool and tennis courts, all with low quarterly HOA dues. Don't wait, schedule your showing now, and make this your dream home today!
